creator: ChambApp
descriptionHtml:
ChambApp is the first mobile job application for the Spanish-speaking market in New York.

ChambApp functions as an employment agency in New York City. We’ve helped thousands of people get jobs.

With ChambApp you can get a job that fits your needs quickly and securely. Browse through a lot of available jobs for free and get hired within minutes.

We have a lot of jobs available in:

• Restaurants
• Delis
• Diners
• Coffee Shops
• Pizzerias
• Construction
• House cleaning
• Supermarkets
• Warehouse
• And many more!

With ChambApp you can easily create your own profile and filter jobs by:

• Position
• Schedule
• Location
• Pay
• Language

ChambApp charges for its placement services and guarantees you a job or gives you a refund!
